<html>
<head>
    <title>One Piece Characters</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-image: url("images/one-piecegif.gif");
            background-size: cover;
            color: white;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 3rem;
        }

        .character {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 30%;
            margin: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .character img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .character h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        }

        footer p, footer a {
            color: white;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        footer a {
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to the One Piece Universe</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="character">
            <img src="images/Luffy-PNG-File.png" alt="Monkey D. Luffy">
            <h2>Monkey D. Luffy</h2>
            <p>The captain of the Straw Hat Pirates. Dreams of becoming the Pirate King.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="character">
            <img src="images/Zoro-PNG-Cutout.png" alt="Roronoa Zoro">
            <h2>Roronoa Zoro</h2>
            <p>A master swordsman and first mate of the crew. Dreams of becoming the greatest swordsman.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="character">
            <img src="images/nami.png" alt="Nami">
            <h2>Nami</h2>
            <p>The crew's navigator. Dreams of drawing a complete map of the world.</p>
        </div>
    </main>
